sources.title: Spirit of Youth 1938 (Biography, Drama, Sport) Joe Louis, Clarence Muse, Edna Mae Harris
sources.description:
The story of the rise of boxer Joe Thomas, which paralleled the life of Joe Louis.

Director: Harry L. Fraser (as Harry Fraser)
Writer: Arthur Hoerl (original screenplay)
Stars: Joe Louis, Clarence Muse, Edna Mae Harris & Mantan Moreland
Genres: Classics, Biography, Drama, Sport
